case_circumstances: Skeletal remains found buried in yard near this residence.  Believed to be Mr. Olaf Holt, 92 years old , a former resident of the residence who died (Natural?) in 1978 and his wife buried him someplace near the home.  Police never found him.  She later died and the new owner discovered the remains.  Mr. Holt has no family for a DNA source, no teeth for dental and no witnesses that knew him are still available.  Pathologist mentions remains having arthritic changes of an elderly man.  No missing persons has been found to match the skeletal remains.
